{"text_id":108423,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," introduce"," and"," investigate"," a"," linear"," pre","-","metric"," electro","dynamics"," framework"," for"," the"," deduction"," of"," the"," light"," cone","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," provide"," a"," more"," fundamental"," and"," unified"," description"," of"," electromagnetic"," phenomena",","," which"," led"," us"," to"," reconsider"," the"," conventional"," metric"," structure"," of"," spacetime",".","\n\n","The"," key"," idea"," of"," our"," approach"," lies"," in"," the"," separation"," of"," the"," metric"," and"," conformal"," structures"," of"," spacetime",","," allowing"," for"," a"," more"," flexible"," and"," encompassing"," formalism","."," Consequently",","," we"," develop"," a"," novel"," pre","-","metric"," theory"," of"," electro","dynamics"," based"," on"," a"," linear"," connection",","," which"," recovers"," the"," metric"," structure"," and"," light"," cone"," through"," additional"," physical"," assumptions",".","\n\n","Our"," main"," results"," reveal"," the"," inherent"," connection"," between"," the"," linear"," connection","'","s"," curvature"," and"," the"," emergence"," of"," the"," light"," cone","."," Specifically",","," we"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," light"," cone"," emerges"," as"," a"," particular"," case"," when"," specific"," constraints"," are"," imposed"," on"," the"," curvature"," tensor","."," These"," constraints"," are"," physically"," interpreted"," as"," the"," vacuum"," electromagnetic"," equations",","," which"," highlight"," the"," intimate"," relationship"," between"," geometry"," and"," electro","magnetism",".","\n\n","Our"," methodology"," combines"," the"," tools"," of"," modern"," differential"," geometry"," with"," physical"," insights"," from"," classical"," electro","dynamics","."," We"," employ"," a"," connection","-","based"," approach",","," contrasting"," with"," the"," traditional"," metric","-","based"," formalism","."," This"," geometric"," viewpoint"," enables"," us"," to"," uncover"," new"," features"," and"," relationships"," within"," the"," foundations"," of"," electro","dynamics",","," shedding"," light"," on"," the"," origins"," of"," the"," light"," cone"," and"," offering"," novel"," perspectives"," on"," spacetime"," structure","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}